 red;\">點解改變呀，你地無做錯對你地班屎忽鬼來講，我剩係想消滅你地咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"4b173d7bc0c29bb24a01b30be8136723ec2823f2","tid":2054373,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T06:55:33.000Z","msg":"人棄我取<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ecc4151e343dbfbac2705b633b8bcd8373a849c","tid":2054373,"uid":70786,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T06:56:24.000Z","msg":"郭蔭庶成個黑警樣<br />\n都唔知做過幾多唔見得光嘅事先上到位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7db36ea0a76d8b6ca7d7367c354f7636dde8198d","tid":2054373,"uid":89641,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T07:01:49.000Z","msg":"800件低能殺人犯預備軍"},{"pid":"fe2e28cfaff9a56c8439b728cae349b9d652c060","tid":2054373,"uid":9193,"like":15,"dislike":3,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T07:03:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"044b7e40644525fb8f208b25227221cea1c0a088","tid":2054373,"uid":3241,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T07:05:22.000Z","msg":"猶太佬比人屠果時都有人願意做猶太警察， 協助納粹送自己人去死"},{"pid":"0886fd12e2e02c227eea04cbaddd5adb3369aeeb","tid":2054373,"uid":284429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T07:08:32.000Z","msg":"總之公我贏字你輸啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"222469789fd22ac1ceda71aa20c68d35ce0d9f49","tid":2054373,"uid":284429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T07:08:32.000Z","msg":"總之公我贏字你輸啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8e2a890fd611fe57fe2d00dfec6acad6